imdb.plot outline: On this lovely show, you get to listen to the wonderful tales of Baron Morbid and his awesome co-host Jacques Strap through the public domain horror movies. Follow their wacky adventures and watch the short films they sometimes provide. Plus, Jacques' video game segment that comes in later in the show. The Break Room doesn't exist.
